<div class="text-center container" >
    <h1 class="display-4">Ski Lessons by Danny</h1>
    <img src="~/assets/img/me-on-hike.jpeg" width="300" height="400" />
    <p>Hi, I'm Danny. This is me on a nice summer hike. When it's not summer, I love to ski! Ever since I was a young lad, my dad took me to the mountains of California to learn the art of pow shredding.
