        because it had been so long since the last time. But eventually, I could do green runs, and then blue runs. Now that I'm living in Utah,
        I get to be close to the mountains and work my way up to those black diamonds.
    </p>
    <br />
    <img src="~/assets/img/ski-example.jpg" width="400" height="300" />
